OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FThe first documents relating to Lord
OL,7,FPeter Mandelson's appointment as
OL,8,Fambassador to the United States will
OL,9,Fbe released on Wednesday.
OL,11,FCabinet minister Darren Jones said a
OL,12,F"big number" of the documents will be
OL,13,Freleased, although it is only expected
OL,14,Fto be a fraction of the papers
OL,15,Fdemanded by Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
