OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FLast month, MPs ordered the government
OL,7,Fto release tens of thousands of
OL,8,Fdocuments relating to Lord Mandelson's
OL,9,Fappointment in 2024 after questions
OL,10,Fover how the peer was vetted, plus
OL,11,Fwhat was known about his links to
OL,12,Fconvicted paedophile Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister has insisted Lord
OL,15,FMandelson "lied repeatedly" to No 10
OL,16,Fabout his relationship with Epstein,
OL,17,Fbefore and during his tenure as
OL,18,Fambassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FChief Secretary to the Prime Minister,
OL,7,FMr Jones, will confirm the release of
OL,8,Fthe first set of documents ` those
OL,9,Fwhich have been cleared for
OL,10,Fpublication by the police
OL,11,Finvestigating Lord Mandelson ` in a
OL,12,FCommons statement.
OL,14,FThe timing of the release has led to
OL,15,Faccusations from the Conservatives
OL,16,Fthat the Prime Minister is attempting
OL,17,Fto "dodge questions" about Lord
OL,18,FMandelson's vetting by publishing the
OL,19,Fdocuments after PMQs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FShadow Cabinet Office minister Alex
OL,7,FBurghart said: "His fingers are all
OL,8,Fover this. He's already admitted that
OL,9,Fhe knew about Mandelson's ongoing
OL,10,Frelationship with Epstein when he
OL,11,Fappointed him.
OL,13,F"Time and again his judgment has been
OL,14,Ffound wanting."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FBut Mr Jones said: "We were always
OL,7,Fteed up to report in early March with
OL,8,Fthe first tranche of documents, which
OL,9,Fis what we're doing this afternoon.
OL,11,F"Because I run the Cabinet Office, at
OL,12,Fthe centre of government, it was
OL,13,Falways my responsibility to give those
OL,14,Fupdates to the House of Commons and
OL,15,Fstatements always come after Prime
OL,16,FMinister's Questions."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FThe release of the documents was
OL,7,Fordered when MPs backed a "humble
OL,8,Faddress" motion tabled by the Tories,
OL,9,Fa rarely-used manoeuvre which compels
OL,10,Fthe government to act.
OL,12,FSome files will be withheld for
OL,13,Fnational security or foreign relations
OL,14,Freasons, but the final say over which
OL,15,Fdocuments are redacted rests with
OL,16,FParliament's Intelligence and Security
OL,17,FCommittee.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,FThe government has also agreed a
OL,7,Fframework with the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fon which documents can be released
OL,9,Fwithout prejudicing the ongoing police
OL,10,Finvestigation into Lord Mandelson.
OL,12,FMr Jones said: "It's a big number of
OL,13,Fdocuments. The government takes its
OL,14,Fresponsibility to be transparent to
OL,15,FParliament really seriously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,F"And of course, on this issue of Peter
OL,7,FMandelson and his relationship with
OL,8,FJeffrey Epstein, we all have a shared
OL,9,Finterest in bringing some
OL,10,Faccountability and transparency to
OL,11,Fthese issues.
OL,13,F"So the first tranche will be
OL,14,Fpublished this afternoon. A second
OL,15,Ftranche, they will come later, because
OL,16,Fthere's been further work that we've
OL,17,Fhad to do across government in
OL,18,Fresponse to the humble address, which
OL,19,Fis not quite ready.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773245483
OL,3,CNo 10 set to release first tranche of
OL,4,CMandelson files on Wednesday
OL,6,F"And we have two other processes that
OL,7,Ftake a bit of time, given the live
OL,8,Fcriminal investigation with the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police and the role of
OL,10,Fthe Intelligence and Security
OL,11,FCommittee in Parliament has some
OL,12,Foversight of it."
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was arrested on
OL,15,FFebruary 23 on suspicion of misconduct
OL,16,Fin public office, having been accused
OL,17,Fof passing sensitive information on to
OL,18,FEpstein during his time as business
OL,19,Fsecretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
